accessibility.text: Finally, the flight attendant joins them and steps into place. She looks into the camera with a confident and professional smile and says, \"AND KEEP EXPERIENCES SAFE IN THE OVERHEAD COMPARTMENT.\" As she speaks, all the flight attendants point upward toward the sky, even higher than the highest Everest peak.

As if showing where they point, the camera slowly pans upward and into the clouds, where we see the aeroplane approaching. With a lateral shot, it follows a KLM plane as it glides gracefully across the sky. In the end, we hear the final line: \"IF YOU GO, MAKE IT MEMORABLE.\"
